00:18:45.680 --> 00:18:46.460
Sawa Eisaku.

00:18:46.580 --> 00:18:47.860
O que queres?

00:18:54.320 --> 00:18:55.210
Coronel Saw.

00:18:55.390 --> 00:18:57.990
